 set ph_num=null	Error Code: 1175. You are using safe update mode and you tried to update a table without a WHERE that uses a KEY column. 
 To disable safe mode, toggle the option in Preferences -> SQL Editor and reconnect.	0.016 sec


to solve this write this statement : SET SQL_SAFE_UPDATES = 0;
Disable safe update mode for the current session:
By setting SQL_SAFE_UPDATES to 0, you can bypass the safe update mode temporarily.
However, exercise caution when using this option, as it removes the safety check for all subsequent UPDATE statements in the session.

